{"tid":1687084,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"有無可能開個民間國際廣播電台","createTime":"2019-11-01T14:50:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-19T18:12:21.000Z","uid":194523,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"28c4f0c8c789a41acae86fc751ad9bb88e79f77a","tid":1687084,"uid":194523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"國際廣播，又稱對外廣播，是指向非本國的聽眾進行的廣播，有多種目的類型，例如新聞傳播、文化交流、也有的是政治宣傳。其以電台廣播為大宗，但也有電視廣播。在大部分情況下，一般通過短波波段進行，對鄰國有時也使用中波波段進行廣播。同時還使用衛星和互聯網進行廣播。<br />\n(according to Wikipedia)<br />\n<br />\n其實有無可能眾籌開一個以短波廣播嘅民間國際廣播電台，向外國傳播香港發生乜野事？"},{"pid":"f68194a6feaace0adae3a2666da109ec4ebf23ab","tid":1687084,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:51:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jSO2Qd4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjSO2Qd4.gif&h=b2e98198&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39fe420392c379a35e4b168bf7f4fcb5dddf51ba","tid":1687084,"uid":194523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:19:22.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cb3977c537ce0eaff8c2a309e48a35c734822516","tid":1687084,"uid":54684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:20:39.000Z","msg":"好難有效果<br />\n<br />\n反而應該係有連登仔搞既Twitter page放料<br />\n亦方便大家retweet<br />\nTwitter有用好多"},{"pid":"7033f4b56ffed49d14119cd3e1bcf75a32b142cf","tid":1687084,"uid":25424,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:23:52.000Z","msg":"互聯網年代已經攪死左好多傳統媒體<br />\n<br />\n你仲用返電台廣播<br />\n係咪弱鳩智<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3516b374dae8014c02016259718c8ca4df4461c1","tid":1687084,"uid":271365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28c4f0c8c789a41acae86fc751ad9bb88e79f77a","tid":1687084,"uid":194523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T14:50:33.000Z","msg":"國際廣播，又稱對外廣播，是指向非本國的聽眾進行的廣播，有多種目的類型，例如新聞傳播、文化交流、也有的是政治宣傳。其以電台廣播為大宗，但也有電視廣播。在大部分情況下，一般通過短波波段進行，對鄰國有時也使用中波波段進行廣播。同時還使用衛星和互聯網進行廣播。<br />\n(according to Wikipedia)<br />\n<br />\n其實有無可能眾籌開一個以短波廣播嘅民間國際廣播電台，向外國傳播香港發生乜野事？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:25:10.000Z","msg":"個人認為<br />\n而家唔係好多人會聽定時嘅廣播<br />\n<br />\n倒不如每日做個短嘅新聞簡報片（60-90秒）（有能力可以做AM 同 PM兩個版本）<br />\n將重要嘅消息傳播出去（亦方便網上流轉）"},{"pid":"5ed96d048154ce3c73bc4878538057cc29d9b81e","tid":1687084,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:36:30.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"a6847bc877e1327dc8bda60fbd92325c6a8195a2","tid":1687084,"uid":133159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T15:47:36.000Z","msg":"我諗好小人聽電台"},{"pid":"4ef593bd8f5bc80062dfe9f7b968a6be8d7a29b7","tid":1687084,"uid":194523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:15:21.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"6c8e192f26f3ae01947eb8e79a716c0794cb7793","tid":1687084,"uid":194523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T21:54:10.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"56a19726c5db477d66355ca9effb1dc1a6d85382","tid":1687084,"uid":194523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:10:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9166b63b5929b853acdb56508c68464e96040648","tid":1687084,"uid":194523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-03T00:54:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ea0fdd267479ab818b388d228ae369c04b6d41bf","tid":1687084,"uid":148497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-19T18:12:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}